graph TD
    A[Client Request] -->|"Provides Anchor GPS Coordinates & Target Area"| B(ClusterBoundaryManager)
    B -->|"Calculates 5-Mile Driving Radius Box"| C(SiteDiscoveryEngine)
    C -->|"Fetches Raw Public Land Data"| D{SiteEvaluator}
    
    D -->|"Scores: Beauty, Water, Privacy"| E(ScoringMatrix)
    D -->|"Scores: Cost, Openness"| E
    D -->|"Scores: Road Access, Bear Risk, Connectivity"| E
    
    E -->|"Applies 0.5x to 3.0x Weights"| F(WeightedCompositeGenerator)
    F -->|"Compiles Site Data"| G(YamlStorageBroker)
    G -->|"Writes to src/spots/target_area/cluster_name/site_name.yaml"| H[Persistent Storage]